casebody.data:
Carlton Paul BACON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2054 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 20, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Following review of appellant's response to this Court's order to show cause, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed for lack of jurisdiction.
